# Supabase project for the online leaderboard.
# Find these values at https://supabase.com/dashboard → your project → Project Settings → API.
# The anon key is designed to be public; Row-Level Security policies (see README) restrict what it can do.
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in your values for local dev.
# For production (GitHub Pages deploy), set the same variables as repo secrets named
#   SUPABASE_URL and SUPABASE_ANON_KEY (see .github/workflows/deploy.yml).

VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-ref.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJ...your-anon-key
